page.title: 19A DAY AT HOLY APOSTLES SCH'L
page.content: 9:00 SCHOOL STARTS 9:05 REGISTRATION 9:10 HYMN PRACTICE WITH HEADMASTER 9:45 GET BOOKS OUT.DO MATHS,FORESTRY OR DOMESDAY PROJECT ON COMPUTER.CLASS DIVIDED INTO 2 GROUPS.1 GROUP DOES FORESTRY,1 DOING MATHS. 10:35 PEOPLE GET MILK AND GET READY TO PACK UP THEIR STUFF FOR PLAYTIME. 11:00 PLAYTIME.11:20 EVERYBODY SWAPS AROUND AND DOES WHAT THEY HAVE NOT ALREADY DONE.11:50 GET READY FOR DINNER.12:00 DINNER TIME! 12:20 PLAYTIME.SOME PEOPLE HAVE RECORDERS.1:00 AFTERNOON REGISTRATION.1:05 CYCLING PROFICIENCY ONLY 4th YEARS DIVIDED INTO 2 GROUPS 1 BEFORE LAST PLAY AND 1 AT 2:20. 2:00 AFTERNOON PLAY. 2:20 2nd GROUP DOES CYCLING PROFICIENCY. 3:08 CYCLING PROFICIENCY ENDS SCIENCE AND ART ENDS 3:15 SCHOOL ENDS
